{
  "id": "adv_main_03_09_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章44話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "っ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gah…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8333333493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 2.101224462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんが……琴乃ちゃんに、平手打ち……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan… slapped Kotono-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.101224462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.1308388471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "渚……なんのつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa… What are you trying to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1308388471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.5293421744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……今、自分がやってることが\n本当に正しいって思ってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan… Do you really think\nwhat you’re doing is right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3319273509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.897210566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの……っ……\n正しいと思ってるから、ここにいるんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… Gah…\nOf course I think it’s right‚ that’s why I’m here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3000000792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.6383897461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、なんで私達の目を見ようとしないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why won’t you look us in the eye?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6383897461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.8733784991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "どんな道を進もうとしても、琴乃ちゃんが\n自信を持ってその道を選んだのなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what path you choose‚\nif you chose it with confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.473106531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.6849221227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "たとえどれだけ辛かったとしても\n受け入れて応援しようと思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it’s hard‚\nI was planning to accept it and support you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.773106531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.48517189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……今の琴乃ちゃんを見てたら\nとても応援なんて出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… When I look at you now‚\nthere’s no way I can support you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0064398644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.0064398644
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.3656255401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなこと言われたって、私はもう引き返せない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even if you say that‚ I can’t turn back anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3656255401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなを傷付けた\nどうやったって償えないくらいのことをした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hurt everyone.\nI did something I can never atone for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333334125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.1197979288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "それでも前に進まなきゃいけないから\n私は……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have to move forward‚ so…\nI…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1333334125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.7522242543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7522242543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.4350484685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4350484685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 70.9801668045
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.9801668045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは琴乃ちゃんなりに\nきっと沢山頑張ってきたんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure you’ve been working hard\nin your own way‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3714843986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 76.1254278061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "誰よりも一番近くで見てきたんだもん\nそれくらい分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been watching you closer than anyone else.\nI know that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8381510652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "渚……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7362894731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.7362894731
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.6300052083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "でも……それだけ頑張ってるのに、私達の目を\n見れないような負い目があるなんて……間違ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… you’ve been working so hard‚ and yet you feel\nso guilty that you can’t look us in the eye… that’s wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 94.1643591004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "絶対に……間違ってる\nだから、その間違いを……私達が正してみせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s absolutely… wrong.\nSo we’re going to correct that mistake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2652031856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 104.5817054189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "さっき言ってたよね\n私達がどりきゅんに勝てないって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said it earlier‚ right?\nThat we can’t beat DoriKyun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 110.5420907415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが抜けて四人になった私達が\nただ弱くなっただけだと思った？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You thought we just got weaker\nnow that we’re a four-member group without you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3985365189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 117.2666667459
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 119.0079736469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "……ふざけないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Don’t be ridiculous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0079736469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_04-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "私達は……私達だって、もう……\n琴乃ちゃんがいた頃の四人じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We… we’re not…\nthe same four-member group we were when you were here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5985492347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 129.3972284235
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 135.3000021137
    },
    {
